archimate:TechnologyService.documentation:
1) Mark data as unused either

a) Manually...

https://druid.apache.org/docs/latest/operations/api-reference.html#post-1
POST /druid/coordinator/v1/datasources/{dataSourceName}/markUnused

https://druid.apache.org/docs/latest/operations/api-reference.html#delete
DELETE /druid/coordinator/v1/datasources/{dataSourceName}/segments/{segmentId}
DELETE /druid/coordinator/v1/datasources/{dataSourceName}

b) Using rules...

https://druid.apache.org/docs/latest/operations/api-reference.html#retention-rules
POST /druid/coordinator/v1/rules/{dataSourceName}

2) Then delete it manually
https://druid.apache.org/docs/latest/operations/api-reference.html#delete
DELETE /druid/coordinator/v1/datasources/{dataSourceName}/intervals/{interval}
